name: agdelte-store
include: .
depend:
  standard-library
-- Domain-agnostic embedded store: NatMap, IndexedMap, length-prefix+CRC Wire
-- codec, WAL (walTxn/recovery), a parameterized Txn monad, and a self-contained
-- FFI (MVar/modifyMVarMasked + durable WAL file ops). Depends ONLY on the
-- standard library — usable by any domain (CRM, the video platform, …).
